    <item>
      <title>斯塔默领导的工党赢得英国大选，结束了保守党 14 年的统治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/starmer-s-labour-wins-uk-election-ending-14-years-of-tory-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 领导的工党赢得了英国大选，并且有望在选票统计中赢得议会绝大多数席位，这一结果颠覆了里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的保守党垮台后的英国政局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/starmer-s-labour-wins-uk-election-ending-14-years-of-tory-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 03:54:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国大选改革浪潮中奈杰尔·法拉奇赢得议会席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/nigel-farage-wins-parliament-seat-amid-reform-uk-election-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[脱欧派人士奈杰尔·法拉奇首次赢得英国议会席位，这为他在英国大选后夺取保守党政权提供了强有力的平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/nigel-farage-wins-parliament-seat-amid-reform-uk-election-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:36:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登进入 2024 年大选的关键周末</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/biden-heads-into-make-or-break-weekend-for-2024-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登即将迎来他政治生涯中最重要的一个周末，他知道他必须恢复选民、捐助者和对他的敏锐度深表怀疑的党内官员的信心 — — 并且任何失误都将对他的连任竞选造成致命影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/biden-heads-into-make-or-break-weekend-for-2024-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:33:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国男子因刺伤党魁被判处 15 年有期徒刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/south-korean-man-sentenced-to-15-years-for-stabbing-party-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国法院以刺伤主要反对党领袖的罪名判处一名男子 15 年监禁，这是该国近年来最引人注目的政治暴力案件之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/south-korean-man-sentenced-to-15-years-for-stabbing-party-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:30:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以下是英国保守党大人物落选的统计数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-election-latest-list-of-conservative-cabinet-ministers-and-others-who-lost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英国政坛，现任内阁部长在选举中落败的情况极为罕见，以至于 1997 年保守党国防部长早早落败被称为保守党的“波蒂略时刻”。保守党在进入今年的选举时担心，他们可能会在一夜之间遭遇数次失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-election-latest-list-of-conservative-cabinet-ministers-and-others-who-lost</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:27:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗总统决选：改革派与极端伊斯兰主义者对决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/iran-presidential-election-pezeshkian-faces-off-against-jalili-in-runoff-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗总统决选将于周五举行，此次选举中唯一的改革派候选人马苏德·佩泽什基安 (Masoud Pezeshkian) 将与反西方伊斯兰主义者赛义德·贾利利 (Saeed Jalili) 角逐政府首脑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/iran-presidential-election-pezeshkian-faces-off-against-jalili-in-runoff-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国大党领导人称，莫迪领导的印度人民党因反对派的强大势力而“动摇”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/modi-s-bjp-shaken-by-stronger-opposition-says-congress-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位资深反对党领袖表示，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪和其他执政党领导人对印度新近壮大的反对党感到不安，反对党目前计划利用其在议会中扩大的影响力，在多个方面向印度人民党发起挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/modi-s-bjp-shaken-by-stronger-opposition-says-congress-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大批准嘉能可煤炭交易，泰克计划回购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/glencore-s-teck-coal-unit-deal-is-said-to-near-canada-approval</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大已批准嘉能可公司（Glencore Plc）以 69 亿美元收购泰克资源有限公司（Teck Resources Ltd.）的冶金煤业务，后者宣布回购 20 亿美元股票并承诺提高铜产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/glencore-s-teck-coal-unit-deal-is-said-to-near-canada-approval</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 23:38:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏格兰民族党遭受重创，工党有望大获全胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/uk-election-snp-pays-price-for-turmoil-in-scotland</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四晚间发布的英国出口民意调查显示，苏格兰民族党有望取得十多年来最差的选举成绩，这进一步削弱了该党推动再次举行独立公投的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/uk-election-snp-pays-price-for-turmoil-in-scotland</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:40:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国股指期货上涨，英镑持稳，工党有望赢得大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/pound-steady-as-labour-projected-to-win-majority-in-uk-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[出口民意调查显示工党将有明确的授权履行其加强经济稳定的承诺，英国股指期货上涨，英镑维持近期涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/pound-steady-as-labour-projected-to-win-majority-in-uk-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:08:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
